name: The Accused
description:
The addiction towards light-emitting diodes has always been involved inside The Orsaw culture. The Upsider, beings that are known to live above the gritty void, believes that The Void is the corporeality site where beings belong when they misnomer their conscience through power abuse by infringing the pre-existing intention of data utilization provided by other beings. This impure conscience will determine The Accused to be consumed by the never-ending data storm and transformed into a melancholic dust cloud which ushers to the assumed formation of memory detritus, random access melancholia, and unused hardware that float towards the unknown nothing. Nothing is ever good if it is too much.

54 seconds drunkloop, somewhere on gudang selatan, Bandung.
